snippet.title: Ale Abbey | Early Access | RELEASE DATE ANNOUNCEMENT
snippet.description:
Welcome to Ale Abbey!

Build and expand your monastery, craft recipes and brew holy ales in this unique brewery tycoon!

Ale Abbey enters Early Access on Steam on the 18th of February 2025!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2789460/Ale_Abbey/
